WEBVTT

00:01.160 --> 00:03.299
PREVIOUSLY ON "SALEM"...

00:03.330 --> 00:04.661
-G|oriana: DO YOU EVER WONDER?
-Cotton: WHAT?

00:04.700 --> 00:05.894
Gloriana:
IF WE COULD LEAVE THIS PLACE?

00:05.930 --> 00:08.433
[ LAUGHS ]

00:09.570 --> 00:11.299
Cotton:
GLORIANA, YOU MUSTN'T BE HERE.

00:11.340 --> 00:13.479
Gloriana:
WHAT WILL YOU DO HERE --

00:13.510 --> 00:14.829
IN THE HOUSE OF THE LORD?

00:16.110 --> 00:17.702
[ GROANS ]

00:21.180 --> 00:22.989
John: WHAT THE HELL
ARE YOU DOING HERE, HOOKE?

00:23.020 --> 00:24.840
William:
NOW, CAREFUL, CAPTAIN --
UNLESS YOU DO NOT MIND ME

00:24.890 --> 00:28.519
TELLING THE GOOD PEOPLE OF SALEM
JUST WHO JOHN ALDEN REALLY IS.

00:28.560 --> 00:30.778
THE PACKAGE SHALL BE YOURS
BY MIDNIGHT.

00:34.060 --> 00:35.425
[ GASPS ]

00:42.870 --> 00:44.906
Mary: THE FAMILIAR
HAS BEEN CUT FROM HER.

00:44.940 --> 00:46.271
Titu ba: HOW?

00:46.310 --> 00:47.834
Mary: AN EXORCISM --

00:47.880 --> 00:50.075
PERFORMED BY
HER DOLT OF A FATHER, NO DOUBT.

00:50.110 --> 00:51.873
SO WE MUST REPLACE IT.

00:51.910 --> 00:53.616
Cotton: MY GOD.

00:53.650 --> 00:56.380
Mary: THE GIRL HAS BEEN RENDERED
FRAIL BY HER CIRCUMSTANCE.

00:56.420 --> 00:57.887
SHE NEEDS
BUT A MOMENT OF REST.

00:57.920 --> 00:59.911
AFI'ER WHICH,
SHE WILL AGAIN BE STRONG ENOUGH

00:59.960 --> 01:00.949
TO POINT THE FINGER.

01:00.990 --> 01:02.127
Mary: OPEN YOUR MOUTH.

01:02.160 --> 01:03.582
George: [ GROANS ]

01:03.630 --> 01:05.029
Mercy: [ SCREAMING ]

01:05.060 --> 01:07.893
I KNOW WHAT YOU ARE.

01:09.470 --> 01:11.461
[ UP-TEMPO MUSIC PLAYS ]

01:11.500 --> 01:13.889
[ WOMEN MOANING ]

01:15.840 --> 01:18.104
Mab: GET 'EM INTO A ROOM,
WILL YA?

01:18.140 --> 01:19.539
I'LL BE BACK IN TWO SHAKES.

01:19.580 --> 01:20.808
Gloriana: YOU'RE LEAVING?

01:20.840 --> 01:23.104
Mab: [ SIGHS ]
ARE YOU DEAF, GIRL?

01:23.150 --> 01:25.106
GET 'EM INTO A ROOM!

01:25.150 --> 01:26.879
Gloriana: YES, MUM.

01:26.920 --> 01:29.070
[ MOANING CONTINUES ]

01:32.320 --> 01:35.380
[ LAUGHTER IN DISTANCE ]

01:35.420 --> 01:37.320
[ INSECTS CHIRPING, DOG BARKS ]

01:54.510 --> 01:55.636
[ BRANCH SNAPS ]

02:31.410 --> 02:34.470
Ancient Witch #1:
[ SPEAKING ANCIENT DIALECT ]

02:37.650 --> 02:39.652
Mr. Hale: I DO NOT.

02:39.690 --> 02:43.626
Ancient Witch #1:
YO'A'NES JOHN ALDEN.

02:43.660 --> 02:45.821
Ancient Witch #2: JOHN ALDEN.

02:45.860 --> 02:47.657
Mr. Hale: YES?

02:58.170 --> 03:00.832
YES. YES.

03:15.290 --> 03:18.384
YET, YOU SAY THE MAN
WHO HOLDS THE SECRET IS DEAD.

03:28.900 --> 03:31.437
ARE WE CERTAIN WE CAN TRUST HER?

03:36.580 --> 03:40.346
I'M NOT SO SURE
THE SERVANT IS LOYAL.

03:40.380 --> 03:43.110
Tituba: I USED TO THINK
YOUR STUBBORNNESS A VIRTUE.

03:43.150 --> 03:44.947
Mary:
AND YOU DON'T ANY LONGER?

03:44.990 --> 03:48.187
Tituba: WHY GO ALONE WHEN
THERE IS INFLUENCE IN NUMBERS?

03:48.220 --> 03:50.279
Mary:
THE GIRL HAS SHOWN HER COLOR.

03:50.330 --> 03:52.457
WE ARE WELL BEYOND
THE POINT OF INTIMIDATION.

03:52.500 --> 03:55.856
Tituba: THEN PERHAPS WE ARE
AT THE POINT OF ELIMINATION.

03:55.900 --> 03:58.391
Mary: PERHAPS,
BUT FOR THE TIME BEING,

03:58.430 --> 04:02.093
SHE IS WORTH MUCH MORE
TO US ALIVE THAN DEAD.

04:05.240 --> 04:06.832
[ "CUPID CARRIES A GUN" PLAYS ]

04:12.850 --> 04:15.614
* POUND ME THE WITCH DRUMS

04:15.650 --> 04:17.208
* WITCH DRUMS

04:17.250 --> 04:19.855
* POUND ME THE WITCH DRUMS

04:21.120 --> 04:23.725
* POUND ME THE WITCH DRUMS

04:23.760 --> 04:25.125
* THE WITCH DRUMS

04:25.160 --> 04:27.720
* BETI'ER PRAY FOR HELL

04:27.760 --> 04:33.039
* NOT HALLELUJAH

04:52.290 --> 04:53.382
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

04:57.390 --> 05:00.325
Rev. Lewis: LOOK WHO'S HERE,
MERCY -- MRS. SIBLEY.

05:00.360 --> 05:01.952
-SIT UP STRAIGHT, GIRL.
-Mary: LEAVE US.

05:03.170 --> 05:04.489
LEAVE US, REVEREND.

05:04.530 --> 05:05.690
Rev. Lewis: YES.

05:05.730 --> 05:08.164
CERTAINLY.

05:08.200 --> 05:10.668
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

05:14.580 --> 05:17.378
Mary: YOU CAME TO VISIT ME
LAST NIGHT.

05:17.410 --> 05:18.775
Mercy: DID I?

05:18.810 --> 05:22.211
Mary: THE TIME FOR COYNESS
HAS PASSED.

05:22.250 --> 05:26.983
IT IS CLEAR YOU KNOW
EXACTLY WHO AND WHAT I AM.

05:27.020 --> 05:29.989
THE ONLY QUESTION THAT REMAINS

05:30.030 --> 05:32.453
IS WHAT YOU WILL DO
WITH THAT INFORMATION.

05:32.500 --> 05:36.391
Mercy: THAT DEPENDS ON YOU,
MRS. SIBLEY.

05:40.440 --> 05:42.863
Mary: WHAT DO YOU WANT, GIRL?

05:42.910 --> 05:45.367
Mercy: I WANT IT TO STOP --

05:45.410 --> 05:50.507
THE TORTURE, THE TORMENT,
THE SUFFERING.

05:52.050 --> 05:53.847
OR I WILL TELL THEM.

05:53.880 --> 05:58.044
I WILL TELL THEM ALL
WHO AND WHAT YOU ARE.

05:58.090 --> 06:01.184
Mary:
YOU KNOW NOTHING OF ME...

06:01.220 --> 06:05.759
OR WHAT I'VE DONE OR GIVEN UP
OR ENDURED

06:05.790 --> 06:07.428
TO BE WHO I AM.

06:09.530 --> 06:13.933
YOU ARE TORTURED
BECAUSE YOU RESIST.

06:13.970 --> 06:17.701
GIVE IN TO ME,
AND YOU WILL KNOW ONLY PLEASURE.

06:17.740 --> 06:21.403
Mercy:
[ Crying ] YOU TORTURE ME.

06:21.440 --> 06:24.045
YOU PUT THE SNAKE INSIDE OF ME.

06:24.080 --> 06:26.674
YOU ARE THE HAG
THAT BITES MY SHOULDER.

06:26.720 --> 06:29.075
Mary:
CAREFUL, OR YOUR FOOLISHNESS

06:29.120 --> 06:32.715
WILL COME TO OVERSHADOW
YOUR USEFULNESS.

06:33.920 --> 06:36.684
YOU LIVE STILL...

06:36.730 --> 06:39.255
BECAUSE I ALLOW IT.

06:39.290 --> 06:42.396
YOU BREATHE
ONLY BECAUSE I WISH IT.

06:44.130 --> 06:46.166
Mercy: YOU WOULD KILL ME?

06:47.940 --> 06:49.862
Mary: IF YOU SPEAK.

06:49.910 --> 06:53.903
STAY SILENT, AND YOU SHALL LIVE.

06:58.450 --> 07:02.739
MY HEART IS DEEP AND FULL.

07:02.790 --> 07:07.887
IT YEARNS TO GIVE YOU FURTHER
CHANCE TO PROVE YOUR WORTH.

07:07.920 --> 07:11.526
FAIL ME, AND YOU FAIL YOURSELF.

07:13.960 --> 07:16.622
THE CRAG AWAITS YOUR DECISION.

07:36.020 --> 07:39.046
John: [ GRUNTING ]

07:42.690 --> 07:45.124
[ BREATHES SHARPLY ]

07:45.160 --> 07:47.856
DAMN IT.

08:19.760 --> 08:21.728
[ GASPING ]

08:32.680 --> 08:33.669
[ GRUNTS ]

08:35.210 --> 08:36.973
[ GASPING ]

08:37.010 --> 08:39.001
[ SIZZLING ]

08:45.720 --> 08:48.257
[ HORSE WHINNIES ]

08:48.290 --> 08:50.850
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS
IN DISTANCE ]

08:56.260 --> 08:59.024
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

09:12.080 --> 09:14.116
Gloriana: YOU SENT FOR ME?

09:14.150 --> 09:16.948
-Cotton: YES.
-G|oriana: [ SIGHS ]

09:16.990 --> 09:19.083
IF YOUR PURPOSE
IS FURTHER HUMILIATION

09:19.120 --> 09:22.510
OR PROBINGS OF THE HEART,
I, FOR ONE, HAVE HAD MY FILL.

09:22.560 --> 09:25.449
Cotton:
MY PURPOSE IS A PROPOSITION.

09:27.000 --> 09:31.198
A BUSINESS ARRANGEMENT OF SORTS.

09:31.230 --> 09:33.232
Gloriana: I'M LISTENING.

09:34.570 --> 09:36.037
Cotton:
IN WHICH YOU WOULD TELL ME

09:36.070 --> 09:39.301
THE SUM OF YOUR MOST FRUITFUL
WEEK'S BOUNTY,

09:39.340 --> 09:43.606
AND I SHALL PROVIDE DOUBLE
IN PERPETUITY...

09:43.650 --> 09:47.768
FOR YOUR COMPANY...

09:47.820 --> 09:51.745
AND YOUR PRECIOUS TIME...

09:51.790 --> 09:53.587
IN EXCLUSIVITY.

10:00.660 --> 10:04.426
Gloriana:
SO YOU WISH TO BUY ME OUTRIGHT.

10:04.470 --> 10:07.132
Cotton: I'M AN ONLY CHILD.

10:08.600 --> 10:10.807
I NEVER LEARNED TO SHARE.

10:10.840 --> 10:14.276
Gloriana:
WHICH IS AS CLOSE AS A MAN
LIKE YOU COMES TO AN APOLOGY.

10:16.950 --> 10:20.442
WAS IT REALLY SO VERY PAINFUL
FOR YOU TO SEE ME WITH ANOTHER?

10:22.280 --> 10:23.713
Cotton: YES.

10:38.570 --> 10:40.993
WILL YOU BE MINE?

10:42.670 --> 10:45.400
Gloriana:
[ BREATHES SHARPLY]

11:03.030 --> 11:04.327
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

11:04.360 --> 11:06.225
-John: COTTON.
-G|oriana: [ GASPS ]

11:06.260 --> 11:08.751
Cotton: CAPTAIN ALDEN!

11:10.600 --> 11:11.999
[ BOTH BREATHING HEAVILY ]

11:12.030 --> 11:13.839
WHAT BRINGS YOU HERE?

11:13.870 --> 11:16.498
[ CHUCKLES ]

11:20.380 --> 11:22.632
John: THIS.

11:22.680 --> 11:25.046
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

11:27.580 --> 11:30.413
Elizabeth: ARE YOU SURE, DO'ITIE?
ARE YOU SURE SHE WON'T HURT US?

11:30.450 --> 11:33.385
Dottie:
'COURSE SHE WON'T HURT US...

11:34.620 --> 11:36.383
UNLESS YOU BE A WITCH.

11:36.420 --> 11:39.025
-Emily: Shh!
-Dottie: [ CHUCKLES ]

11:41.700 --> 11:43.292
HELLO, MERCY.

11:48.640 --> 11:52.360
MAY WE COME IN?

11:53.640 --> 11:55.631
Mercy: MM.

12:05.120 --> 12:07.884
Dottie: THEY COME TO YOU
IN YOUR ROOM, MERCY?

12:07.920 --> 12:11.083
THEM. . .WITCHES?

12:12.830 --> 12:15.219
Mercy: SOMETIMES...

12:17.830 --> 12:20.469
AND OTHER TIMES IN OTHER PLACES.

12:25.110 --> 12:27.431
Elizabeth:
ARE THEY HERE WITH US NOW?

12:27.480 --> 12:29.277
CAN YOU SEE THEM AS WE SPEAK?

12:29.310 --> 12:31.608
Mercy:
NO, I DON'T SEE THEM NOW.

12:31.650 --> 12:34.118
Emily: DO THEY HURT YOU?

12:34.150 --> 12:36.277
Mercy: SOMETIMES.

12:36.320 --> 12:38.117
Emily: WHAT'S IT LIKE?

12:39.190 --> 12:40.953
Mercy: WHAT'S IT LIKE?

12:40.990 --> 12:42.878
Emily: TO POINT YOUR FINGER

12:42.930 --> 12:45.490
AND MAKE THEM SHAKE
AND TREMBLE WITH FEAR.

12:45.530 --> 12:48.294
Dottie: TO POINT YOUR FINGER
AND WATCH THEM RUN.

12:50.430 --> 12:52.466
Mercy:
NO, IT'S NOT LIKE THAT...

12:52.500 --> 12:53.933
AT ALL.

12:53.970 --> 12:56.097
I SWEAR.

12:56.140 --> 12:58.438
Emily: NO WOMAN IN SALEM
HAS EVER HAD THAT KIND OF POWER.

12:58.470 --> 13:01.337
Dottie: NOT EVEN MARY SIBLEY.

13:16.360 --> 13:18.328
Mercy:
YOU THINK I HAVE SWAY...

13:18.360 --> 13:20.123
Dottie: [ CHUCKLES ]

13:20.160 --> 13:23.197
Mercy: ...AMONGST ALL THE PEOPLE
OF SALEM?

13:23.230 --> 13:26.620
Emily: YOUR LITI'LE FINGER POINTS
TO LIFE A-AND DEATH ITSELF.

13:26.670 --> 13:31.130
Elizabeth: TELL US --
WHAT DO THE WITCHES LOOK LIKE?

13:31.170 --> 13:32.808
Mercy: MM.

13:32.840 --> 13:34.876
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

13:36.880 --> 13:38.700
Richards:
ONE MORE THING, MRS. SIBLEY --

13:38.750 --> 13:40.945
THERE WAS AN OVERFLOW OF PARCELS
LEFI' ON THE BRITANIA,

13:40.980 --> 13:43.847
ALL OF WHICH ARE TO BE DELIVERED
TO A WILLIAM HOOKE.

13:43.890 --> 13:45.346
NOW, WE'VE LOOKED HIGH AND LOW.

13:45.390 --> 13:46.880
NO ONE COULD SEEM
TO LOCATE THE FELLOW.

13:46.920 --> 13:49.013
Mary: I SEE.
I'LL TAKE CARE OF IT.

13:49.060 --> 13:51.119
Richards: THANK YOU, MADAM.

13:51.160 --> 13:54.220
Tituba: THEY WILL NOT FIND
MR. HOOKE -- NOT NOW, NOT EVER.

13:54.260 --> 13:56.490
Mary: I WON'T ASK
WHAT HAPPENED TO HIM.

13:56.530 --> 13:58.020
Tituba: NOR SHOULD YOU.

13:58.070 --> 14:00.231
Mary: THEN CONTAIN IT
BEFORE CURIOSITY GROWS.

14:00.270 --> 14:04.058
Mr. Hale: UH, MRS. SIBLEY,
UH, GOOD AFI'ERNOON.

14:04.110 --> 14:06.362
MIGHT I BORROW YOUR GIRL?

14:06.410 --> 14:10.005
THE MISSUS HAS TAKEN ILL
WITH A BATCH OF WAYWARD MUSSELS

14:10.050 --> 14:14.919
AND NOW BEGS RELIEF WITH ONE
OF HER EXCEPTIONAL TONICS.

14:14.950 --> 14:18.886
Mary: PLEASE SEND MRS. HALE
MY MOST URGENT REGRETS.

14:18.920 --> 14:20.911
Mr. Hale: MOST KIND.

14:20.960 --> 14:22.882
MM?

14:27.360 --> 14:30.397
Mary: OH, MR. RICHARDS,
UH, FETCH FOR ME A LIST OF ITEMS

14:30.430 --> 14:32.421
THIS MR. HOOKE WAS HERE
TO RECEIVE,

14:32.470 --> 14:34.734
ONE THAT ALSO PERHAPS INCLUDES
THEIR SITE OF ORIGIN.

14:34.770 --> 14:36.362
Richards: RIGHT AWAY, MADAM.

14:36.400 --> 14:39.608
Tituba: YOUR LIE IS CLUMSY.
NO ONE IS ILL.

14:39.640 --> 14:42.029
MY MISTRESS CAN SEE THAT
AS CLEARLY AS I.

14:42.080 --> 14:44.708
Mr. Hale: YES, WELL, WHEN
IT COMES TO LIES AND SUBTERFUGE,

14:44.750 --> 14:47.275
I DEFER TO YOUR
EXPERT ENDOWMENTS.

14:47.320 --> 14:49.777
Tituba: STATE YOUR PURPOSE
OR BE GONE WITH YOU.

14:49.820 --> 14:54.689
Mr. Hale: MY PURPOSE IS
TO RID THIS TOWN OF JOHN ALDEN

14:54.720 --> 14:56.210
ONCE AND FOR ALL,

14:56.260 --> 15:00.094
UNLESS THAT IS A PURPOSE
FOR WHICH YOU LACK INTEREST.

15:03.000 --> 15:04.968
[ DOG BARKING ]

15:10.570 --> 15:12.868
John:
THAT WAS THE SAME GIRL --

15:12.910 --> 15:15.572
FROM LAMB'S,

15:15.610 --> 15:17.475
THE ONE YOU THREW A PUNCH OVER.

15:17.510 --> 15:19.569
Cotton: WAS IT?

15:19.610 --> 15:23.114
John: WASN'T AWARE
THEY MADE OUTCALLS.

15:24.850 --> 15:27.250
Cotton:
TELL ME AGAIN OF THE VISIONS.

15:29.790 --> 15:32.179
John: YELLOWED FACES...

15:33.600 --> 15:38.663
...BODIES OVERCOME BY RASH
AND BLISTER...

15:38.700 --> 15:40.964
DEATH IN GREAT NUMBERS.

15:41.000 --> 15:44.458
Cotton:
AND THIS CAME TO YOU AS THE
ARTIFACT WAS BROUGHT TO LIFE?

15:44.510 --> 15:46.808
John: YEP.

15:46.840 --> 15:48.728
Cotton:
WHERE DID YOU SAY IT CAME FROM?

15:48.780 --> 15:51.806
John: WHERE EVERYTHING IN THIS
TOWN COMES FROM -- A SHIP.

16:01.960 --> 16:03.825
Cotton: RITUM MAGNI.

16:07.960 --> 16:09.518
John: THE GRAND RITE?

16:09.560 --> 16:13.860
Cotton: MOST OF WHAT WE KNOW
IS LORE -- RUMOR, LEGEND.

16:13.900 --> 16:16.266
IT SAYS THIS OBJECT,
THIS "MALUM,"

16:16.300 --> 16:17.665
HAS THOUGHT TO BE PRESENT

16:17.710 --> 16:19.530
AT EVERY GRAND RITE
THROUGHOUT HISTORY.

16:19.570 --> 16:22.038
EVERYTHING I HAVE READ HAS SAID
THAT THE GRAND RITE

16:22.080 --> 16:24.674
HAS ONLY EVER BEEN ATTEMPTED,
NEVER COMPLETED.

16:24.710 --> 16:26.849
John:
MAYBE PLAGUE'S ONLY PART OF IT.

16:26.880 --> 16:28.677
Cotton:
THIS OBJECT IS EVIL.

16:28.720 --> 16:32.110
IT CONSECRATES THE EARTH
FOR THE DEVIL'S RETURN.

16:32.150 --> 16:34.516
John: IT WAS HERE FOR DELIVERY.
SOMEONE WAS EXPECTING IT.

16:36.560 --> 16:39.188
Cotton: A WITCH.

16:39.230 --> 16:41.323
WE MUST INFORM THE SELECTMEN
IMMEDIATELY.

16:42.560 --> 16:44.164
John: NO.

16:44.200 --> 16:45.724
Cotton: NO?

16:45.770 --> 16:48.364
John: WE HAVE SOMETHING
THE WITCHES WANT.

16:48.400 --> 16:50.368
WHAT BE'I'I'ER WAY
TO GET THEIR ATTENTION?

16:50.410 --> 16:52.799
Cotton: WHAT BE'I'I'ER WAY
TO GET YOURSELF KILLED?

16:52.840 --> 16:54.671
John: WE ARE ALL IN DANGER,

16:54.710 --> 16:59.079
BUT I WOULD RATHER DIE BEFORE
SALEM'S FINEST CONTROL MY FATE.

17:02.580 --> 17:04.241
ARE YOU WITH ME?

17:06.590 --> 17:08.558
[ RAT SQUEAKING ]

17:12.260 --> 17:15.821
Mr. Hale: NOT OVER THERE,
YOU INFERNAL MUTANT! OVER HERE!

17:15.860 --> 17:18.021
[ INSECTS BUZZING ]

17:31.980 --> 17:34.710
THAT'S HIM.

18:19.260 --> 18:22.297
Mary: AND THE MAGISTRATE'S TRUE
PURPOSE IN TAKING YOU FROM ME?

18:22.330 --> 18:24.992
Tituba:
MY EYES BETRAYED MY SENSE

18:25.030 --> 18:28.830
WHEN I CAME UPON MRS. HALE
BENT OVER HER CHAMBER POT.

18:30.810 --> 18:33.677
Mary:
IF YOU INSIST UPON THIS LIE,

18:33.710 --> 18:35.337
IT FORCES ME TO ASK

18:35.380 --> 18:38.975
WHERE YOU'RE OFF TO NOW
WITH SUCH GREAT URGENCY.

18:39.010 --> 18:41.444
Tituba: THE APOTEK.

18:41.480 --> 18:44.779
I RUN LOW ON THE BARK
OF CASCARA SAGRADA.

18:48.020 --> 18:49.351
Mary: BY ALL MEANS.

19:06.410 --> 19:08.833
Dottie: IT'S LIKE THE GREAT
FLOWING ROBE OF THE POPE.

19:08.880 --> 19:11.474
Elizabeth: OR THE JEWELED-UP
CROWN OF A KING.

19:11.510 --> 19:14.445
Mercy: WELL, IT'S QUITE
DISAGREEABLE ON -- I ASSURE YOU.

19:14.480 --> 19:16.710
Dottie: JUST THINK OF IT --

19:16.750 --> 19:20.413
BEING LED THROUGH MARKET
BY THE HANDSOME REVEREND MATHER.

19:22.490 --> 19:24.219
WHAT'S HE LIKE, MERCY, HMM?

19:24.260 --> 19:26.854
DOES HE SPEAK OF GOD AND DEMONS?

19:26.890 --> 19:29.199
Mercy:
WE'VE SPOKE MANY TIMES.

19:29.230 --> 19:32.859
HE'S SHOWN GREAT INTEREST
IN MY AFFLICTION.

19:32.900 --> 19:34.197
Elizabeth: IT'S YOU
WHO POINTS THE FINGER...

19:34.240 --> 19:36.037
[ LAUGHTER ]

19:36.070 --> 19:39.198
Emily: ...WHILE ALL OF SALEM
HOLDS THEIR BREATH AND WAITS.

19:39.240 --> 19:42.869
Mercy: WELL, IT'S NOT
EXACTLY LIKE THAT. I...

19:42.910 --> 19:46.402
Emily: IF I HAD YOUR SAY-SO,
I KNOW WHO I'D ACCUSE.

19:46.450 --> 19:48.247
Mercy: WHO?

19:52.790 --> 19:54.382
WHO?

19:56.790 --> 19:58.326
Dottie: IT'S HER FATHER.

19:58.360 --> 20:01.249
SHE'D ACCUSE HER OWN FATHER.

20:03.900 --> 20:05.788
Mercy: WHY?

20:11.270 --> 20:14.034
Dottie: MAKES HER SING
IN THE STREETS ALL DAY LONG

20:14.080 --> 20:16.935
WHILE HE NURSES THE BO'ITLE
AT LAMB'S --

20:16.980 --> 20:18.845
SING AND BEG.

20:18.880 --> 20:22.839
THEN HE TAKES WHAT COIN
SHE'S MADE FOR SPIRITS

20:22.880 --> 20:26.611
AND BEATS HER SENSELESS
FOR HER TROUBLES.

20:28.790 --> 20:30.985
Mercy: IS THIS TRUE?

20:32.730 --> 20:35.198
Emily:
I'M TO BE 15 NEXT MONTH,

20:35.230 --> 20:39.291
AND HE SWEARS
TO SELL ME TO THE ROD.

20:42.140 --> 20:44.904
Mercy: YOUR FATHER MEANS
TO SELL YOU TO THE WHOREHOUSE?

20:44.940 --> 20:47.272
Emily:
[ Crying ] I'LL RUN AWAY.

20:47.310 --> 20:51.406
EVEN IF HE SELLS ME,
I'M -- I'LL RUN.

20:54.750 --> 20:57.310
Mercy:
NO ONE IS RUNNING AWAY.

20:57.350 --> 20:59.614
NO ONE.

20:59.650 --> 21:01.982
[ CLANGING ]

21:02.020 --> 21:06.286
Hawker: SINNER OR SAVIOR!
HOW ARE WE TO KNOW?!

21:06.330 --> 21:09.219
LOOK BUT TO THE TORMENT
OF THE DAMNED,

21:09.260 --> 21:13.435
AND THINK WELL OF THE DIFFERENCE
BETWIXT ANGELS AND DEVILS,

21:13.470 --> 21:18.567
AND YOU WILL KNOW WHAT SIN IS
AND WHERE SIN RESIDES!

21:18.610 --> 21:21.932
John: HOW 'BOUT YOU NOT RILE
THE CROWD FURTHER THAN THEY ARE?

21:21.980 --> 21:24.642
Hawker: [ CHUCKLES ]
IT'S TWO BITS A SHEET.

21:24.680 --> 21:28.946
I'M STILL FULL UP HERE,
UNLESS YOU'D LIKE TO BUY ME OUT.

21:28.980 --> 21:32.040
John: BE LOADS MORE FUN
TO BEAT YOU STUPID.

21:33.290 --> 21:34.518
MISS HALE.

21:34.560 --> 21:37.188
Anne: CAPTAIN ALDEN.

21:37.220 --> 21:38.858
John: IT'S A FINE DAY.

21:38.890 --> 21:40.494
Anne: [ SIGHS ] IS IT?

21:40.530 --> 21:42.452
John: PERHAPS NOT.

21:42.500 --> 21:44.491
Anne:
OH, INDEED. PERHAPS NOT.

21:44.530 --> 21:47.499
PERHAPS THERE WILL BE
NO MORE FINE DAYS IN SALEM.

21:47.540 --> 21:50.759
PERHAPS THE DAYS OF FINE DAYS
ARE TRAGICALLY BEHIND US.

21:50.810 --> 21:55.008
John:
HAVE I OFFENDED YOU, MISS HALE?

21:58.380 --> 22:00.769
Anne:
DO YOU CONSIDER IT OFFENSIVE

22:00.820 --> 22:03.175
RAISING HOPE IN A HEART
MOST NORMALLY WELL-GUARDED

22:03.220 --> 22:05.188
WHILE YOUR OWN BEATS
IN THE BREAST OF ANOTHER?

22:05.220 --> 22:07.142
DO YOU, CAPTAIN ALDEN,
FIND THAT REPREHENSIBLE

22:07.190 --> 22:08.680
-OR AS SIMPLY UNKIND?
-John: WELL, I --

22:08.720 --> 22:11.120
Anne: OR, MOST LIKELY,
YOU THINK NOT OF IT AT ALL

22:11.160 --> 22:13.549
OR ME OR OTHERS, AS IS THE WONT
AND PRACTICE OF MOST MEN.

22:14.530 --> 22:16.157
AH, MRS. SIBLEY.

22:17.500 --> 22:18.728
Mary: ANNE.

22:18.770 --> 22:20.192
Anne: PERFECT.

22:20.230 --> 22:21.697
[ HORSE WHINNIES ]

22:21.740 --> 22:23.367
[ SIGHS ]

22:23.410 --> 22:27.801
Mary: ARE YOU EVER GRATEFUL
TO BE NO LONGER YOUNG?

22:27.840 --> 22:29.831
John: [ SCOFFS ]

22:29.880 --> 22:31.905
YES.

22:31.950 --> 22:36.341
THOUGH HER YOUTHFUL MOXIE
DOES BRING TO MIND ANOTHER.

22:36.380 --> 22:39.679
Mary:
I WAS NEVER THAT YOUNG.

22:41.260 --> 22:44.752
John: WE WERE BOTH...ONCE.

22:49.430 --> 22:51.762
WHAT BRINGS YOU TO MARKET?

22:51.800 --> 22:53.222
Mary: TITUBA.

22:53.270 --> 22:55.761
WE WERE TO MEET
AT THE HERBALIST.

23:12.090 --> 23:15.389
Tituba: A FINE PAIR YOU TWO MAKE
IN THIS PLACE OF DEATH.

23:15.420 --> 23:16.580
Mr. Hale: GIVE IT TO HER.

23:20.800 --> 23:22.552
Tituba: IT WILL TAKE TIME.

23:22.600 --> 23:25.194
Mr. Hale: AND YOU WILL REPORT TO
ME AS SOON AS YOU'RE FINISHED.

23:25.230 --> 23:27.221
Tituba: AFRAID TO STAY?

23:27.270 --> 23:30.899
Mr. Hale: MY TIME
IS BETTER SPENT ELSEWHERE.

23:30.940 --> 23:33.477
Tituba: FOR THE BEST.

23:33.510 --> 23:35.808
ONCE A MAN DABBLES
IN THE DARK ARTS,

23:35.840 --> 23:38.843
IT'S DIFFICULT FOR HIM
TO RETURN TO THE LIGHT.

23:40.250 --> 23:42.138
FETCH ME A RABBIT.

23:42.180 --> 23:44.114
Ghoul: Y-YES.

23:46.090 --> 23:48.752
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

23:48.790 --> 23:51.384
Man: GET ON THERE!

23:51.430 --> 23:53.250
Rose: MRS. SIBLEY.

23:53.290 --> 23:54.393
Mary: MRS. BROWNING.

23:54.430 --> 23:56.648
Rose: OH. NO NEED TO TURN AWAY.

23:56.700 --> 23:59.225
HE IS AN ARRESTING FIGURE.

23:59.270 --> 24:03.764
ONLY MY OLD LADY'S EYES THAT
KEEP ME FROM STARING MYSELF.

24:03.810 --> 24:06.461
Mary: DON'T BE RIDICULOUS.

24:06.510 --> 24:09.138
Cotton: YOU STILL INSIST
ON IGNORING MY EXPERTISE.

24:09.180 --> 24:10.579
John: YEP.

24:10.610 --> 24:12.271
Cotton:
THERE ARE LESS PEDESTRIAN,

24:12.310 --> 24:13.914
LESS PAIN FUL METHODS,

24:13.950 --> 24:16.510
WITH WHICH WE COULD ACCOMPLISH
OUR GOALS.

24:17.950 --> 24:21.158
IT MUST HAPPEN TONIGHT.
THERE WILL BE NO SECOND CHANCES.

24:21.190 --> 24:25.126
John: THE WAYS OF THE COMMON
ARE ALWAYS GOOD ENOUGH FOR ME.

24:28.360 --> 24:33.059
AND IF IT CAUSES PAIN,
SO MUCH THE BETTER.

24:34.300 --> 24:36.632
Mr. Hale:
STILL IN A BROWN STUDY, I SEE.

24:36.670 --> 24:39.104
Mrs. Hale:
HASN'T SPOKEN A WORD ALL DAY.

24:39.140 --> 24:41.279
Mr. Hale:
MM. WELL, SHE'LL RECOVER.

24:41.310 --> 24:42.629
Mrs. Hale: FROM WHAT?

24:42.680 --> 24:44.705
-WHAT DID YOU SAY TO HER?
-Mr. Hale: NOTHING.

24:44.750 --> 24:48.208
MERELY TRYING TO SPARE HER HEART
THE INEVITABLE WOE.

24:48.250 --> 24:51.117
Mrs. Hale:
WORRY NOT, MY HUSBAND.

24:51.150 --> 24:52.708
THIS WILL ALL BE DISTANT MEMORY

24:52.750 --> 24:54.980
ONCE SHE'S BECOME
MRS. COTTON MATHER.

24:55.020 --> 24:57.853
Mr. Hale: MM-HMM.

24:59.530 --> 25:01.452
Rose: I WONDER.

25:01.500 --> 25:03.195
Mary: WONDER WHAT?

25:03.230 --> 25:07.997
Rose: IF HE'D NEVER LEFT,
IF YOU'D BEEN ALLOWED TO MARRY,

25:08.040 --> 25:11.498
AND FOUND YOURSELF NOW
IN THAT HOUSE OF HIS

25:11.540 --> 25:14.202
WITH THREE SQUALLING BRATS,

25:14.240 --> 25:17.846
WORKING CEASELESSLY TO SPREAD
YOUR MEAGER WAGES...

25:17.880 --> 25:22.749
WOULD CAPTAIN ALDEN STILL HOLD
SUCH DESPERATE APPEAL?

25:25.190 --> 25:29.081
OR IS IT THAT YOU'RE TRAPPED
IN FIRST BLISS,

25:29.120 --> 25:32.578
ROMANCE FROM WHICH
THERE'S NO ESCAPE,

25:32.630 --> 25:34.689
YOUR HEART EVER HURTING

25:34.730 --> 25:38.063
FROM THE IMAGININGS
OF WHAT COULD HAVE BEEN?

25:40.270 --> 25:44.366
DO NOT STARE AT HIM IN PUBLIC.
IT WEAKENS YOU.

25:47.210 --> 25:49.678
Mary: IT NEVER EVEN OCCURS
TO YOU, DOES IT?

25:49.710 --> 25:54.545
I MIGHT HAVE OUTGROWN
YOUR SAGE ADVICE.

25:54.580 --> 25:55.911
[ CLANGING ]

25:59.920 --> 26:02.309
Mercy: [ GROWLING ]

26:07.290 --> 26:09.895
Dottie:
THOUGH SHE CANNOT SPEAK...

26:09.930 --> 26:12.467
Girls:
...SHE WILL SHOW US THE WITCH!

26:12.500 --> 26:14.593
SHE WILL SHOW US THE WITCH!

26:19.010 --> 26:20.432
Tituba:
BALBIN, GAB, GABOR, AGABA!

26:20.470 --> 26:22.074
ARISE, I CALL THEE!

26:22.110 --> 26:26.046
COLPRIZIANA,
OFFINA ALTA NESTRA,

26:26.080 --> 26:27.911
FUARO MENUT.

26:27.950 --> 26:30.714
WILLIAM HOOKE,
THOU ART THE DEAD I SEEK.

26:30.750 --> 26:33.116
WILLIAM HOOKE,
ANSWER MY CALLING.

26:33.150 --> 26:34.913
Girls:
SHE WILL SHOW US THE WITCH!

26:34.960 --> 26:36.587
Dottie:
THOUGH SHE CANNOT SPEAK...

26:36.620 --> 26:38.884
Girls:
...SHE WILL SHOW US THE WITCH!

26:38.930 --> 26:40.158
Mercy: [ SNARLS ]

26:40.190 --> 26:41.794
Girls:
SHE WILL SHOW US THE WITCH!

26:41.830 --> 26:43.320
SHE WILL SHOW US THE WITCH!

26:43.360 --> 26:45.828
SHE WILL SHOW US THE WITCH!

26:45.870 --> 26:47.428
SHE WILL SHOW US THE WITCH!

26:47.470 --> 26:51.008
Mercy: [ SCREAMING ]

26:51.040 --> 26:54.237
[ CROWD MURMURING ]

26:54.280 --> 26:57.329
[ SCREAMING CONTINUES ]

27:01.950 --> 27:04.783
Mary: STOP HER, REVEREND.
SHE MAKES MOCKERY OF YOU.

27:04.820 --> 27:06.742
STOP HER!

27:06.790 --> 27:09.350
Mercy: [ BREATHING DEEPLY ]

27:09.390 --> 27:11.278
[ SCREAMS ]

27:11.330 --> 27:14.424
Tituba: WILLIAM HOOKE,
THOU ART THE DEAD I SEEK.

27:14.460 --> 27:16.599
WILLIAM HOOKE,
ANSWER MY CALLING.

27:16.630 --> 27:18.598
FORTIS ROA,
STRENGTH AND BREATH,

27:18.630 --> 27:20.689
STRENGTH AND BREATH,
STRENGTH AND BREATH.

27:20.740 --> 27:22.958
WILLIAM HOOKE,
THOU ART THE DEAD I SEEK.

27:23.000 --> 27:24.968
WILLIAM HOOKE,
ANSWER MY CALLING.

27:25.010 --> 27:28.969
STRENGTH AND BREATH, STRENGTH
AND BREATH, STRENGTH AND BREATH.

27:35.350 --> 27:36.510
Hooke: YOU.

27:36.550 --> 27:38.643
Titu ba: YES.

27:38.690 --> 27:41.784
Hooke: ITHOUGHT
OUR BUSINESS CONCLUDED.

27:41.820 --> 27:44.880
Tituba:
TELL ME JOHN ALDEN'S SECRET.

27:44.930 --> 27:47.694
Hooke: [ CHUCKLES ]

27:47.730 --> 27:51.120
MEET ME IN HELL, YOU BITCH.

27:51.170 --> 27:53.798
Tituba: OH, THERE ARE WORSE
PLACES THAN HELL.

27:53.840 --> 27:55.398
SPEAK!

27:55.440 --> 27:56.896
Hooke: AHH.

27:58.870 --> 28:01.577
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

28:01.610 --> 28:03.999
Mercy: [ GROWLING ]

28:11.390 --> 28:14.211
[ SCREAMS ]

28:28.400 --> 28:30.595
[ SCREAMS ]

28:33.610 --> 28:36.738
WITCH !

28:36.780 --> 28:40.045
Dottie: OH, NO, EMILY.

28:40.080 --> 28:42.219
IT'S YOUR FATHER.

28:52.560 --> 28:53.925
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

28:53.960 --> 28:55.825
Man: [ GRUNTING ]

29:00.170 --> 29:02.536
Tituba: WHAT'S HAPPENED NOW?

29:02.570 --> 29:05.960
Mr. Hale: QUERY YOUR MISTRESS.
I HAVEN'T THE FAINTEST IDEA.

29:07.670 --> 29:10.844
WHAT OF YOUR MISSION?

29:20.690 --> 29:22.908
Mary:
OF COURSE I FIND YOU HERE,

29:22.960 --> 29:25.827
NOT AT THE JAIL
INVESTIGATING THIS NEW WITCH,

29:25.860 --> 29:27.555
NOT WITH MERCY LEWIS,

29:27.590 --> 29:31.560
BUT HERE, ALONE,
PLAYING WITH YOUR BLASTED TOYS.

29:31.600 --> 29:35.696
Cotton: IT SEEMS I AM DETERMINED
TO DISPLEASE YOU, MRS. SIBLEY.

29:42.380 --> 29:43.938
-Mary: [CRYING]
-Cotton: MRS. SIBLEY.

29:48.180 --> 29:49.977
PLEASE.

29:50.020 --> 29:51.487
-Mary: I'M SORRY.
-Cotton: PLEASE.

29:55.020 --> 29:58.854
TELL ME -- WHAT TROUBLES YOU.

30:00.160 --> 30:04.267
Mary: THAT GIRL HAS GONE MAD
WITH POWER.

30:04.300 --> 30:08.669
ENCOURAGED BY HER PEERS,
INFLUENCED BY PETTY DISPUTE.

30:10.340 --> 30:13.662
THE SELECTMEN FEAR
THAT SHE'S NO LONGER RELIABLE.

30:13.710 --> 30:15.871
Cotton: [ SCOFFS ] NONSENSE.

30:15.910 --> 30:18.845
Mary: THEY ARE UNCERTAIN
THAT SHE CAN BE FURTHER TRUSTED.

30:18.880 --> 30:20.700
Cotton:
IT IS NOT THEIRS TO DECIDE.

30:20.750 --> 30:22.115
I WILL ASSESS THE GIRL

30:22.150 --> 30:24.038
AND FORM MY OWN OPINION
OF HER ROLE.

30:24.090 --> 30:25.785
Mary:
YOU WOULD DO THAT, REVEREND?

30:25.820 --> 30:27.788
Cotton: OF COURSE.

30:27.820 --> 30:29.515
Mary: [ SIGHS ]

30:29.560 --> 30:33.553
I AM TORN AND HARRIED
BY MY MANY RESPONSIBILITIES.

30:33.590 --> 30:36.388
Cotton: [SIGHS]
IT'S MY FAULT COMPLETELY.

30:36.430 --> 30:38.295
Mary: [ SNIFFLES ]

30:38.330 --> 30:40.389
Cotton: I HADN'T CONSIDERED
THE TOLL THIS HAS TAKEN ON YOU.

30:40.430 --> 30:43.968
Mary: OH, AND A RIFT AMONGST THE
SELECTMEN AT THIS FRAGILE MOMENT

30:44.010 --> 30:48.504
MIGHT BE MORE BURDEN THAN I --
OR SALEM -- COULD BEAR.

30:48.540 --> 30:50.337
Cotton:
WORRY NOT, MRS. SIBLEY.

30:50.380 --> 30:53.042
YOU FETCHED ME HERE
TO RUN THESE WITCH TRIALS,

30:53.080 --> 30:55.241
AND RUN THEM I MUST.

30:59.850 --> 31:01.750
Mary: THANK YOU, REVEREND.

31:01.790 --> 31:03.314
WHAT A RELIEF TO FIND

31:03.360 --> 31:06.158
AT LEAST ONE
WHO CAN RELIEVE MY HARDSHIPS.

31:06.190 --> 31:08.397
[ SIGHS ]

31:17.800 --> 31:20.030
WHAT IS THAT?

31:21.610 --> 31:25.546
Cotton: IT'S AN ARTIFACT
THAT I'M RESEARCHING.

31:31.590 --> 31:34.286
Mary:
DOES IT HAVE TO DO WITH WITCHES?

31:34.320 --> 31:37.414
Cotton: IT'S ASSOCIATED
WITH THE GRAND RITE,

31:37.460 --> 31:41.624
A RITUAL OF DEATH ATTRIBUTED
TO WITCHES OVER THE CENTURIES.

31:41.660 --> 31:46.461
Mary: AND WHY DOES THIS OBJECT
IN PARTICULAR CONCERN YOU?

31:47.970 --> 31:51.599
Cotton: EVERYTHING REGARDING
WITCHES CONCERNS ME, MADAM.

31:51.640 --> 31:53.733
WE CANNOT BE TOO PREPARED.

31:53.770 --> 31:56.432
[ CHUCKLES ]

32:04.490 --> 32:08.711
Mary: WHAT LUCK FOR SALEM THAT
YOUR FATHER WAS UNAVAILABLE.

32:08.760 --> 32:11.649
WE WILL OWE OUR FUTURE TO YOU,
REVEREND.

32:11.690 --> 32:14.659
OF THAT I AM SURE.

32:29.280 --> 32:31.248
[ DOOR OPENS ]

32:31.280 --> 32:33.498
[ FOOTSTEPS APPROACH ]

32:36.450 --> 32:38.816
Mr. Hale:
THE SECRET IS USELESS.

32:38.850 --> 32:41.751
JOHN ALDEN WILL NOT LEAVE TOWN
FOR A GAMBLING DEBT.

32:41.790 --> 32:43.519
Rose: [ LAUGHS ]

32:43.560 --> 32:46.028
THAT'S WHAT SHE TOLD YOU?

32:46.060 --> 32:47.857
-Mr. Hale: SHE LIED?
-Rose: [SCOFFS]

32:47.890 --> 32:49.494
Mr. Hale:
I'LL BEAT IT OUT OF HER.

32:49.530 --> 32:50.997
Rose: NO.

32:51.030 --> 32:54.966
DOES TITUBA NOT YEARN
FOR THE GRAND RITE?

32:55.000 --> 32:59.801
IS THERE ANOTHER, IN FACT,
THAT CRAVES IT MORE?

32:59.840 --> 33:02.206
Mr. Hale:
SO SHE'LL USE THE REAL SECRET.

33:02.240 --> 33:05.676
Rose: IN HER OWN WAY,
BUT FOR THE SAME PURPOSE --

33:05.710 --> 33:07.849
TO CONTROL MARY.

33:07.880 --> 33:10.610
Mr. Hale: AH.

33:10.650 --> 33:13.949
Rose: [SIGHS]
WE HAVE ANOTHER PROBLEM.

33:13.990 --> 33:17.619
THE OBJECT WILLIAM HOOKE
WAS TASKED TO DELIVER

33:17.660 --> 33:19.924
HAS FALLEN INTO OTHER HANDS.

33:21.530 --> 33:25.990
Mr. Hale: AND WHAT EXACTLY WAS
WILLIAM HOOKE TASKED TO DELIVER?

33:27.930 --> 33:29.739
Rose: THE MALUM.

33:31.270 --> 33:32.806
Mr. Hale: THE MALUM?

33:32.840 --> 33:35.877
Rose: WE MUST BE PREPARED
FOR EVERY EVENTUALITY,

33:35.910 --> 33:38.401
EVEN ONE THAT DOES NOT INCLUDE
MARY SIBLEY.

33:38.450 --> 33:41.715
THAT IS THE MALUM'S PURPOSE.

33:41.750 --> 33:43.911
Mr. Hale: WHO HAS IT?

33:45.890 --> 33:47.915
Rose: JOHN ALDEN.

34:03.600 --> 34:06.103
Mary:
I LOOKED FOR YOU AT MARKET.

34:06.140 --> 34:08.335
Tituba: THE APOTEK RAN LOW.

34:08.380 --> 34:10.735
I WAS FORCED
TO PICK THE BARK MYSELF.

34:18.920 --> 34:23.755
Mary: THE NEXT LIE TO CROSS
YOUR LIPS WILL BE YOUR LAST.

34:25.560 --> 34:30.156
Tituba: YOU WOULD THREATEN ME,
YOUR ONE TRUE ALLY?

34:31.670 --> 34:33.763
Mary: SO THE OTHERS
HAVE TURNED ON ME.

34:33.800 --> 34:35.233
Titu ba: YES.

34:35.270 --> 34:37.090
Mary: WHO?

34:37.140 --> 34:40.405
Tituba: EACH AND EVERY ONE.

34:40.440 --> 34:41.805
Mary: ROSE?

34:41.840 --> 34:44.070
Titu ba: EVERYONE.

34:44.110 --> 34:47.409
THEY MEET IN SECRET,

34:47.450 --> 34:49.873
SPEAK OF YOUR WEAKNESS,

34:49.920 --> 34:53.481
PLOT TO RID SALEM OF JOHN ALDEN.

34:53.520 --> 34:55.886
Mary: FEARFUL
HE HAS TAKEN ME FROM MYSELF.

34:55.920 --> 34:57.080
Titu ba: YES.

34:57.120 --> 34:58.587
Mary: NONSENSE.

34:58.630 --> 35:00.552
I AM MOST COMPLETELY MYSELF!

35:00.590 --> 35:02.592
Tituba: YOU ARE NOT!

35:02.630 --> 35:05.360
YOU ARE IN LOVE.

35:07.600 --> 35:12.299
LET ME TELL YOU ABOUT HIM --
THIS MAN THAT YOU LOVE.

35:12.340 --> 35:14.308
HE IS A MURDERER.

35:14.340 --> 35:17.070
-Mary: [ SCOFFS ] HE IS NOT.
-Tituba: YES.

35:17.110 --> 35:20.477
AND HE HAS KILLED YET ANOTHER
TO KEEP HIS SECRET.

35:20.510 --> 35:23.911
IF I TELL THE MAGISTRATE,
THE MILITIA WILL COME,

35:23.950 --> 35:26.942
THEY WILL TAKE HIM,
AND THEY WILL HANG HIM.

35:29.060 --> 35:31.324
Mary: LIES.

35:31.360 --> 35:33.920
Tituba: IF YOU WISH
FOR JOHN ALDEN TO LIVE,

35:33.960 --> 35:36.849
YOU WILL COMPLETE
THE GRAND RITE.

35:36.900 --> 35:40.768
THE NEXT MOON WILL SEE
EIGHT MORE DEAD.

35:40.800 --> 35:42.392
Mary: LIES.

35:44.240 --> 35:47.505
Tituba: THE DEAD DON'T LIE.

35:52.910 --> 35:54.775
Emily: HELLO, FATHER.

35:54.820 --> 35:57.209
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS
IN DISTANCE ]

36:00.350 --> 36:02.159
Henry: I'M LOCKED UP.

36:02.190 --> 36:03.817
Emily: YES, YOU ARE.

36:03.860 --> 36:05.487
Henry: WHAT FOR?

36:05.530 --> 36:07.725
Emily: YOU'RE A WITCH.

36:10.260 --> 36:14.128
Henry: A DRUNK, A CARD SHARP,
A TWO-TIMER, MAYBE.

36:14.170 --> 36:16.229
BUT A WITCH?

36:16.270 --> 36:20.161
[ LAUGHING ]

36:20.210 --> 36:23.202
I THINK NOT.

36:23.240 --> 36:26.846
Emily:
I COME TO SAY GOODBYE.

36:26.880 --> 36:31.488
AND THANKS FOR NOTHING.

36:31.520 --> 36:34.819
Henry:
I'LL BE OUT OF HERE IN NO TIME,

36:34.860 --> 36:39.081
AND THEN YOU WILL BE SOLD,
JUST LIKE WE PLANNED.

36:40.590 --> 36:42.899
Emily: OR YOU'LL HANG...

36:42.930 --> 36:46.093
OR BURN.

36:49.070 --> 36:52.562
WE'LL SEE, FATHER.

36:52.610 --> 36:55.579
WE'LL SEE.

36:57.440 --> 36:59.442
Anne: MISS HOPKINS?

37:01.210 --> 37:03.678
Emily: MISS -- MISS HALE.

37:03.720 --> 37:06.541
Anne: A SMALL COLLECTION
TO HELP EASE YOUR CIRCUMSTANCES

37:06.590 --> 37:09.286
IN THIS MOST TRYING TIME.

37:11.760 --> 37:13.751
Emily: THANK YOU.

37:13.790 --> 37:16.122
Anne:
HE'LL GET A FAIR TRIAL.

37:16.160 --> 37:19.095
MY FATHER WILL SEE TO THAT,

37:19.130 --> 37:21.394
OR I'LL SEE TO MY FATHER.

37:23.140 --> 37:24.903
Emily:
YOU'RE MOST KIND, MISS HALE.

37:24.940 --> 37:28.933
Anne: AH, IT'S NOT KINDNESS.

37:33.010 --> 37:36.446
THEY HUNG MY FRIEND.

37:36.480 --> 37:41.110
I WATCHED HER KICK AND...SCREAM

37:41.150 --> 37:44.426
AND...

37:44.460 --> 37:47.258
SOIL HERSELF.

37:50.600 --> 37:52.966
I WILL NOT DO THAT AGAIN.

37:56.640 --> 37:58.608
STAY STRONG.

38:37.040 --> 38:39.372
Mary: TIME FOR TRUTH.

38:49.890 --> 38:52.825
Mary:
I LIED TO YOU EARLIER.

38:52.860 --> 38:55.397
I WAS YOUNG ONCE --

38:55.430 --> 38:59.867
YOUNG ENOUGH
THAT I BELIEVED IN GOODNESS.

38:59.900 --> 39:02.664
I BELIEVED IN IT
BECAUSE I SAW IT IN YOU.

39:02.700 --> 39:06.466
YOU CAN'T HELP IT.
Y-YOU CAN'T STOP IT.

39:06.510 --> 39:09.172
YOU CAN'T BE ANY OTHER WAY.

39:09.210 --> 39:12.748
AND I THINK
THAT'S WHY I LOVED YOU.

39:15.250 --> 39:18.242
IMAGINE MY SURPRISE...

39:18.280 --> 39:22.080
BEING TOLD YOU'RE A MURDERER.

39:25.790 --> 39:28.179
John: YOU DON'T KNOW ME.

39:28.230 --> 39:29.697
Mary: WHAT?

39:30.700 --> 39:33.692
John: YOU DON'T KNOW ME!

39:33.730 --> 39:36.893
-I KILLED 20 MEN.
-Mary: NO.

39:36.940 --> 39:38.532
John: YES. 20 MEN.

39:38.570 --> 39:40.936
AND THEIR ONLY CRIME WAS
THAT THEY HAD COME TO SAVE ME.

39:40.970 --> 39:42.278
Mary: NO, I WON'T BELIEVE IT.

39:42.310 --> 39:45.370
John:
BELIEVE IT BECAUSE IT'S TRUE!

39:45.410 --> 39:47.446
[ BREATHING SHARPLY ]

39:51.490 --> 39:55.119
LUCKY MEN GO TO THEIR GRAVES
WITH NO REGRETS.

39:57.790 --> 40:01.248
BARELY A DAY PASSES
WHEN I DON'T HAVE ONE.

40:03.730 --> 40:05.823
Mary: [ CRYING ]

40:07.930 --> 40:12.037
SOMETIMES IN LIFE,
WE MAKE CHOICES.

40:12.070 --> 40:15.278
AND SOMETIMES, THESE --
THESE DIFFICULT CHOICES --

40:15.310 --> 40:19.076
THEY LEAD US TO DO THINGS,
TERRIBLE THINGS,

40:19.110 --> 40:21.249
AND WE DON'T WISH TO.

40:21.280 --> 40:24.215
WE'D DO ANYTHING NOT TO.

40:24.250 --> 40:26.912
BUT CHOICE INFORMS CHOICE.

40:26.950 --> 40:29.259
YOUR ACTIONS, THOUGH YOUR OWN,

40:29.290 --> 40:31.155
THEY -- THEY DON'T RESEMBLE

40:31.190 --> 40:34.990
ANYTHING YOU'D HAVE WANTED
OR WISHED FOR.

40:35.030 --> 40:37.294
TELL ME THAT IT WAS LIKE THAT,

40:37.330 --> 40:41.118
TELL ME
THAT IT WAS A DIFFICULT CHOICE,

40:41.170 --> 40:45.266
A TERRIBLE THING,
PLEASE, PLEASE,

40:45.310 --> 40:48.108
SO THAT I MIGHT STILL BELIEVE
IN GOODNESS.

40:59.290 --> 41:02.782
John: I MURDERED 20 MEN.

41:02.820 --> 41:05.550
AND I MAKE NO EXCUSES
FOR MYSELF.

41:11.870 --> 41:13.963
WILL YOU HAVE ME ARRESTED?

41:18.710 --> 41:21.463
Mary:
I AM THE ONLY ONE THAT KNOWS.

41:45.670 --> 41:48.025
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS
AND LAUGHTER ]

41:48.070 --> 41:49.958
Girls: PRINCE OF DARKNESS,
MASTER OF ALL,

41:50.000 --> 41:52.207
FATHER OF EVIL, HEAR OUR CALL.

41:52.240 --> 41:54.674
PRINCE OF DARKNESS,
MASTER OF ALL,

41:54.710 --> 41:57.201
FATHER OF EVIL, HEAR OUR CALL.
PRINCE...

41:57.240 --> 41:58.798
[ LAUGHTER ]

41:58.850 --> 42:00.499
Girl: ...FATHER OF EVIL,
HEAR OUR CALL.

42:00.550 --> 42:03.246
Girls: PRINCE OF DARKNESS...

42:03.280 --> 42:05.043
Girl: ...FATHER OF EVIL,
HEAR OUR CALL.

42:05.090 --> 42:07.388
Girl: PRINCE OF DARKNESS,
MASTER OF ALL,

42:07.420 --> 42:09.081
FATHER OF EVIL, HEAR OUR CALL.

42:09.120 --> 42:12.681
PRINCE OF DARKNESS,
MASTER OF ALL...

42:12.730 --> 42:14.254
Girls: PRINCE OF DARKNESS,
MASTER OF ALL,

42:14.290 --> 42:16.895
FATHER OF EVIL, HEAR OUR CALL.

42:16.930 --> 42:19.865
[ LAUGHTER ]

42:19.900 --> 42:23.734
...FATHER OF EVIL,
HEAR OUR CALL!

42:23.770 --> 42:26.364
PRINCE OF DARKNESS,
MASTER OF ALL,

42:26.410 --> 42:29.004
FATHER OF EVIL, HEAR OUR CALL.

42:29.040 --> 42:31.679
PRINCE OF DARKNESS,
MASTER OF ALL,

42:31.710 --> 42:34.372
FATHER OF EVIL, HEAR OUR CALL!

42:34.410 --> 42:36.913
PRINCE OF DARKNESS,
MASTER OF ALL,

42:36.950 --> 42:38.247
FATHER OF EVIL...

43:06.250 --> 43:09.139
Mary: WE HAD A DEAL.

43:09.180 --> 43:12.445
Mercy: OUR DEAL
NO LONGER PLEASES ME.

43:12.490 --> 43:15.880
Mary: THEN IASK AGAIN --

43:15.920 --> 43:18.252
WHAT DO YOU WANT?

43:19.860 --> 43:22.954
Mercy:
I WANT TO BE JUST LIKE YOU.

44:04.040 --> 44:06.167
[ CREAKING ]

44:23.260 --> 44:25.558
Woman: AAH!

44:26.730 --> 44:28.527
[ GUN COCKS ]

